+

+brew install  miniconda
+```
+
+3. Use homebrew to install cmake
+
+```zsh
+brew install cmake
+```
+
+4. Create a new conda environment and install pip
+
+```zsh
+conda create -n qarray python=3.11
+conda install pip
+```
+
+5. Install qarray using pip
+
+```zsh
+pip install qarray
+```
+
